Module org.example.fitnessprojectgui
Package ProjectFitness

Class FitnessClass

java.lang.Object
ProjectFitness.FitnessClass
public class FitnessClass extends Object
Represents a fitness class offered by a gym. Provides constructors for creating classes with all attributes or essential attributes only.
